      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>I already tried talking to people and it just feels like they're following a script, you know? Like they're just saying what they're \"supposed\" to say because they feel bad for me. It doesn't actually change the fact that I'm just a ghost in this place. If I just... stopped, it wouldn't even be a tragedy. It would just be one less person wandering around aimlessly. There's a weird kind of peace in thinking about how easy it would be to just vanish.",
